Serializable, org.apache.wicket.behavior.IBehavior, org.apache.wicket.behavior.IBehaviorListener, org.apache.wicket.behavior.IComponentConfigurationBehavior, org.apache.wicket.IClusterable, org.apache.wicket.IRequestListener, org.apache.wicket.markup.html.IHeaderContributor
public class AjaxAutoSavingBehavior
extends org.apache.wicket.ajax.form.AjaxFormSubmitBehavior

This behavior will submit a form at regular intervals. Any HTML element with class='autosave_info' will display the status of these automatic saves.

See Also:
Serialized Form

protected void onAutoSave(org.apache.wicket.ajax.AjaxRequestTarget target)
